  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help working children during the Covid 19 pandemic</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ecuador has been hit hard by Covid-19 and strict measures have been put in place to contain the spread. Many of the families CENIT supports are no longer allowed to work in the markets and they have  lost the little income they were previously earning. CENIT have temporarily adapted the support they offer. They are now helping children and their families by telephone, providing emotional support, health and other advice, homework assistance, and some food provisions where possible.</narrative>
  </description>
